# Indentation

Use **tab characters** for indentation in source code, not spaces.

This is enforced by the repository root `.editorconfig`:

- C# (`.cs`), Avalonia markup (`.axaml`, `.xaml`), MSBuild (`.csproj`, `.props`), and shell scripts (`.sh`) use `indent_style = tab`.
- YAML, JSON, and Markdown keep spaces (tooling compatibility).

Run `./scripts/format-cs.sh` before committing C# changes. Do not convert leading spaces inside multiline string literals (embedded JSON, prompts, etc.).
